"{\"uid\": \"cbc.ca-books-6-books-that-inspired-olympic-games-primetime-host-perdita-felicien-1.4520004\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"It's summer and the Olympic Games Paris 2024\\u00a0are almost here!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 61, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024\\u00a0will take place from\\u00a0July 26-Aug.\\u00a011\\u00a0and the Paralympic Games happen Aug. 28-Sept. 8.\", \"from\": 62, \"to\": 158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 62, \"end\": 72, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.47777781379326e-11, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Canada will be among the approximately 10,500 athletes representing 206 countries taking part - and\\u00a0CBC is covering all the coverage with live and on-demand content.\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 160, \"end\": 171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9960636690287628, \"rank\": 0.002962631564371055, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perdita Felicien\\u00a0is a two-time\\u00a0Olympian and champion hurdler\\u00a0who is bringing Canadians the action from Paris\\u00a0as the co-host ofOlympic Games Primetime.\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 332, \"end\": 348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perdita_Felicien\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Perdita Felicien\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perdita_Felicien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perdita_Felicien\"}, {\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999972213247427, \"rank\": 2.77852508521205e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.0749697739427469e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can see a complete schedule of events here.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2018, Felicien\\u00a0shared\\u00a0six books that fuelled her love of literature.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Color Purpleis a story about the life of a Black woman in rural Georgia, from her traumatic childhood in the early 1900s to her cathartic reunion with her family 30 years later.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\", \"score\": 0.9978437392158394, \"rank\": 0.001427319416289921, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The novel by Alice Walker won the 1983 Pulitzer Prize for fiction, and was shortly after adapted into a film by Steven Spielberg.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Walker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alice Walker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Walker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Walker\"}, {\"begin\": 900, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2604564289860235e-18, \"text\": \"Steven Spielberg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Is it cheating if I fell in love with the movie first?\\\"\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"asked Felicien.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully not, because by the time I read Walker's book in high school, I loved the story even more.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This was the first time I read a book and hated and loved some of the characters on the page with passion.\\\"\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The hatred I felt for the character of Mister felt real to me.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(To this day I can not stand actor Danny Glover who played the role in the film.)\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Glover\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.111063408415473e-43, \"text\": \"Danny Glover\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Glover\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Glover\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The devotion I felt for Celie was so visceral, that even once I had put the book down, I still felt it.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Also, I had not read anything where a character's dialect was written phonetically.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That pulled me in and allowed me to know Walker's characters even more.\\\"\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1580, \"end\": 1586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\", \"score\": 0.9999996497400093, \"rank\": 3.5025998114495343e-07, \"text\": \"Walker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was in elementary school when I read this book.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"E.B.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"White got me deeply invested in this friendship between a spider and a pig.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But what does he do?\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He kills one of them off.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like, dude?\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was devastation to my itty-bitty heart.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(I cry silently inside even thinking about it\\u00a0today.)\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That book made me feel things, and for that I simply love it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The experience of being a child soldier and living in the midst of a civil war in Sierra Leone are far removed from my everyday life in North America.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2052, \"end\": 2064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sierra_Leone_Civil_War\", \"score\": 0.9814101502137602, \"rank\": 0.018941978260885686, \"text\": \"Sierra Leone\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sierra_Leone_Civil_War\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sierra_Leone_Civil_War\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This true story took me to a place and through horrors I did not know existed.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not put down this story, in which Beah turns from tragedy into personal triumph.\\\"\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ishmael Beah  \\\"Memoir is one of my favourite genres.\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McBride pulled me in with his story of being a Black man in America who was raised by a white mother.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2348, \"end\": 2355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_McBride\", \"score\": 0.9365306573404683, \"rank\": 0.06775784985122368, \"text\": \"McBride\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_McBride\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_McBride\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Not only is his mother extremely entertaining and smart, but she is hiding a part of herself that her children know nothing about.\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not stop turning each delicious page.\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"\\u200b  \\\"I read this book over 10 years ago.\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was pulled in by the plight of the main character Wang Lu, a poor, determined farmer.\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2726, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lutetium\", \"score\": 0.6985543129956493, \"rank\": 0.4290068018344484, \"text\": \"Lu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lutetium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lutetium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Buck won a Pulitzer Prize for it in 1932.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will be picking it back up very soon so I can get reacquainted.\\\"\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This book, set in Nigeria in the 1890s amidst pre- and post-colonial life in West Africa, is filled with adventure.\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2886, \"end\": 2893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9998597744629204, \"rank\": 0.0001402451526924456, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2945, \"end\": 2956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999998654584579, \"rank\": 1.3454137755888677e-07, \"text\": \"West Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Achebe tackles complex themes like identity, colonialism\\u00a0and socio-political issues through rich and multi-layered characters.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This\\u00a0work\\u00a0is a gem.\\\"\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Perdita Felicien's comments have been edited for length and clarity.\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3135, \"end\": 3151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perdita_Felicien\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Perdita Felicien\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perdita_Felicien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perdita_Felicien\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Add some \\\"good\\\" to your morning and evening.\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up for our newsletter.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will send you book recommendations, CanLit news, the best author interviews on CBC and more.\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3361, \"end\": 3364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBC_Television\", \"score\": 0.999821603647617, \"rank\": 0.0001616803319957261, \"text\": \"CBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBC_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBC_Television\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next issue of CBC Books newsletter will soon be in your inbox.Discover all CBC newsletters in theSubscription Centre.\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3394, \"end\": 3403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBC_Arts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBC Books\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBC_Arts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBC_Arts\"}, {\"begin\": 3455, \"end\": 3458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBC_Television\", \"score\": 0.999821603647617, \"rank\": 0.0001616803319957261, \"text\": \"CBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBC_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBC_Television\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and the GooglePrivacy Policyand GoogleTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Audience Relations, CBCP.O.\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Box 500 Station AToronto, ONCanada, M5W 1E6  Toll-free (Canada only):1-866-306-4636  It is a priority for CBC to create products that are accessible to all in Canada including people with visual, hearing, motor and cognitive challenges.\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3731, \"end\": 3734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBC_Television\", \"score\": 0.999821603647617, \"rank\": 0.0001616803319957261, \"text\": \"CBC\", \"types\": [